; Regression test for issue #737: ledger xact does not honour payee tag (BZ#737)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/737
; The xact command should recognize the Payee: tag and match by it,
; but it currently ignores the tag and only matches on the raw payee name.

2024/01/01 Grocery Store
    ; Payee: Supermarket
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test xact Supermarket -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: No accounts, and no past transaction matching 'Supermarket'
end test
